Import bugphyzz

Source: R/bugphyzz.R
importBugphyzz.Rd

importBugphyzz imports bugphyzz as a single data.frame. It includes attributes with categorical and binary (boolean) attributes.

importBugphyzz(version = "devel", force_download = FALSE, v = 0.5)

Arguments

version

Character string. The version to download. Default is 'devel' (current file on the GitHub repo waldronlab/bugphyzzExports).

force_download

Logical value. Force a fresh download of the data or use the one stored in the cache (if available). Default is FALSE.

v

Validation value. Deafult 0.5.

Value

A data.frame.

Examples


bp <- importBugphyzz()
